you know...  I think I may have seen Nevarre a time or two =D   If you are looking for a guild,  let me know =D  you can either e-mail me privately,  or send me a tell in game when you see me next.  You can view the Claws of Night website at www.clawsofnight.org  (we're still working on the site)  The guild has become my extended family =D.

Katashaka Naboombu
OR
Gwenevieve (soon to be Hartripper)

 Kuervodr@... wrot

Nevarre, 33 Barb BST
Anjeles, 20 Human Magician
Fokker, 17 High Elf Enchanter

These are now my new mains, I also have a bunch of lesser alts. For instance a 14th human necro, a 14th half-elf bard, a new 11th vah shir rogue, a 12th gnome cleric,and on and on and on, heh. These are all on Vazaelle

On Rodcet I also have my 49th dark elf sk, a 54th halfling rogue, a 24th dark elf wizard, a 29th barb shaman, a 12th troll beastlord, a new 8th high elf paladin and a few others I cant recall off the top of my head.

This does not count the many characters I have deleted , of course. =)
